        <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Hd1e108">Rubrica 13</head>
        <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De pace seu concordia</head>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e114">
          <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>
          ¶ De pace et concordia. Rubrica. 13
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e119">
          <lb ed="#V" n="13"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e115">Iob histo. c. 22.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e123">Acquiesce omni
            <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>potenti: et habeto pacem:
            <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>et per hoc habebis fructus optimos</quote> 
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e131">
          <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>
          ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e129">Psalmista 33 psalmus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e135">Inquire pa
            <lb ed="#V" n="17" break="no"/>cem et persequere eam.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e142"> /
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e140">36 psalmus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e144">Sunt reliquie
            <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>homini pacifico.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e150"> /
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e150">84. psalmus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e152">Iustitia et pax
            <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>osculate sunt.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e158">
          <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>
          ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e162">Salomon in prouerb. c. 12.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e162">Qui pacis ine
            <lb ed="#V" n="21" break="no"/>unt: consilia sequitur eos gaudium.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e168"> /
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e172">16 ca.</ref>
            <lb ed="#V" n="22"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e170">Cum placuerint domino vie hominis: ini
            <lb ed="#V" n="23" break="no"/>micos quoque eius conuertet ad pacem.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e178">
          <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>
          ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e186">Cronica de nugis philsophurum. c. 7 scilicet de cleobo
            <lb ed="#V" n="25" break="no"/>lo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e182">Cleobolus vnus de septem sapientibus di
            <lb ed="#V" n="26" break="no"/>cebat inimicum amicum faciendum.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e190">
          <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>
          ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e201">Aristoteles ethincorum libro 8. c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e194">Concordia si
            <lb ed="#V" n="28" break="no"/>mile aliquid amicitie videtur esse.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e201">
          <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e214">Iesus filius sirach in eccl. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e205">Prosequa
            <lb ed="#V" n="30" break="no"/>tur te verbum pacis et iustitie.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e211"> /
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e224">25. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e213">Ait ie
            <lb ed="#V" n="31" break="no"/>sus filius sirach. In tribus placitum est spiri
            <lb ed="#V" n="32" break="no"/>tui meo que sunt probata coram deo et hominibus:
            <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>Concordia fratrum et amor proximorum: Et vir
            <lb ed="#V" n="34"/>et mulier sibi conseutientes.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e225"> /
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e240">28. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e227">Memen
            <lb ed="#V" n="35" break="no"/>to nouissimorum: et desine inimicari: tabitudo
            <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>enim et mors imminent in mandatis.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e235">
          <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e254">Salustius in iugurtino:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e239">Concordia praue
            <lb ed="#V" n="38"/>res crescunt: discordia maxime dilabuntur.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e245">
          <lb ed="#V" n="39"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e266">Uirgilius enid. li. 11 circa medium:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e249">Pacem
            <lb ed="#V" n="40"/>laudate sedentes.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e255">
          <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e278">Tullius de amincitia:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e259">Quanta vis amicitie
            <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>concordieque sit ex dissensionibus atque discor
            <lb ed="#V" n="43" break="no"/>diis percipi potest.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e268"> /
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e291">Idem philippicorum lib. 2.</ref>
            <lb ed="#V" n="44"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e270">Nomen pacis dulce est: et ipsa res salutaris. <!--118.xml-->
            <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
            <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>Pax est tranquilla libertas.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e282"> /
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e307">Li. 12 et peni.</ref>
            <lb ed="#V" n="46"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e284">Dulce est nomen pacis: res vero ipsa tum iocun
            <lb ed="#V" n="47" break="no"/>da tum salutaris.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e292">
          <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e321">Ouidius de fastis lib. i.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e296">Pax cerere nutritur
            <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>pacis alumna ceres.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e302"> /
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e330">Libro. 4.</ref>
            <lb ed="#V" n="50"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e304">Pace ceres leta est: et vos orate coloni.
            <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>Perpetuam pacem: pacisicumque ducem.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e312">
          <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>
          ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e344">Quintilianus declam. 8 declam.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e316">Semper
            <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>odiorum honestus occasus est: et dum simulta
            <lb ed="#V" n="54" break="no"/>tes nihil alind habent quam nocendi cupiditatem: spe
            <lb ed="#V" n="55" break="no"/>ciosa in melius animi mutatio est cum exempli honore.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e326">
          <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e360">Mattheus in euangel. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e330">Beati pacifici:
            <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>quoniam ipsi filii dei vocabuntur.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e337"> /
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e371">9. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e339">Ait iesus
            <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>discipulis suis: Pacem habete inter vos.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e345">
          <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e383">Ioannes apostolus in euang.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e349">Ait iesus discipulis
            <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>suis quoniam morti appropiquabat: Pacem relin
            <lb ed="#V" n="61" break="no"/>quo vobis: pacem meam do vobis.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e357">
          <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e397">Petrus apostolus in epistola. i. c. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e361">Qui vult vitam
            <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>diligere et videre dies bonos coherceat lin
            <lb ed="#V" n="64" break="no"/>guam suam a malo et labia sua ne loquantur dolum
            <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>declinet a malo et faciat bonum: inquirat pa
            <lb ed="#V" n="66" break="no"/>cem et sequatur eam.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e373">
          <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e415">Paulus apostolus: epistola ad romanos. c. 18.</ref>
            <lb ed="#V" n="68"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e377">Que pacis sunt sectemur.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e383"> /
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e425">Idem epstola ad
            <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>collossenses. c. 3. et pe.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e385">Pax christi exultet in
            <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>cordibus vestris: in qua et vocati estis in vno
            <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>corpore.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e395"> /
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e440">Idem epistola. 2. ad timotheum. c. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e397">Se
            <lb ed="#V" n="72" break="no"/>ctare iustitiam: fidem: charitatem: pacem.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e404"> /
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e451">Idem
            <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>in epstola ad heb. c. 12.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e406">Pacem sequimini cum omni
            <lb ed="#V" n="74" break="no"/>bus et sanctimoniam: sine qua nemo videbit deum.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e414">
          <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e466">Seneca tragediarum in hercule furente. c. 3</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e418"/> <!--ref but no quote-->
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e422">
          <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>
        ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e426">Pacem reduci velle victori expedit: victo
            <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>necesse est.</quote> <!--quote but no ref-->
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e432"> /
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e487">Idem epistolarum ad lucillum
            <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>libro. 8. epistola. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e434">Non est dubium quin fe
            <lb ed="#V" n="79" break="no"/>licior pax sit nunquam lacessita: quam multo repa
            <lb ed="#V" n="80" break="no"/>rata sanguine.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e444"> /
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e502">Idem de ira libro. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e446">Quid
            <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>est gloriosius quam iram in amiciciam commutare</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e452">
          <lb ed="#V" n="82"/> /
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e514">Idem in prouerbiis:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e456">Pacem cum omnibus
            <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>habeas: bellum cum vitiis: Semper dissensio ab
            <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>alio incipiat a te reconciliatio.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e465">
          <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>
          ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e529">Ualerius maximus libro. 2 titulo de in
            <lb ed="#V" n="86" break="no"/>stitutis antiquis.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e469">Conuiuium solenne maio
            <lb ed="#V" n="87" break="no"/>res instituerunt: idque caristiam appellaue
            <lb ed="#V" n="88" break="no"/>runt: cui preter cognatos et affines nemo
            <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>interponebatur: vt si qua inter necessarias <!--119.xml-->
            <pb ed="#V" n="46-v"/>
            <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
            <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>personas querela esset orta apud sacra men
            <lb ed="#V" n="2" break="no"/>se et inter hylaritatem animorum a fautoribus con
            <lb ed="#V" n="3" break="no"/>cordie tolleretur.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e494"> /
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e559">Li. 4. ti. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e496">Sicut placidum
            <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>mare ex asperso celumque ex nubilo serenum
            <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>hilari aspectu sentitur: sic bellum pace mutatum
            <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>plurimum gaudii affert. Speciosius aliquan
            <lb ed="#V" n="7" break="no"/>do iniurie beneficio vincuntur quam mutui odii
            <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>pertinacia pensantur.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e510">
          <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e579">Prudentius de psicomachia. c. 10.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e514">Pax ple
            <lb ed="#V" n="10" break="no"/>num virtutis opus: pax summa laborum.
            <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>Pax belli exacti precium est: preciumque pericli.
            <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>Nil placidum fine pace deo.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e524">
          <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e595">Prosper. sub vlt. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e528">Insontem vitam pacis
            <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>amator agit.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e534">
          <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e607">Cassiodorus epistolarum li. 4. e. 43.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e538">Non est le
            <lb ed="#V" n="16" break="no"/>ue prudentes viros in pacis instituta pecca
            <lb ed="#V" n="17" break="no"/>re.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e546"> /
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e619">Libro. 11. e. 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e548">Transigite semper inno
            <lb ed="#V" n="18" break="no"/>xii.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e555"> /
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e630">Lib. 12. et fi. e. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e557">Uiri fortes semper in
            <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>pace modesti sunt.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e563">
          <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e642">Isidorus soliloquiorum li. 2. c. 25.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e567">Pacem
            <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>cum omnibus retine.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e573"> /
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e652">26 c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e575">Uiue sper in pace.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e579">
          <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e662">Mattheus vindocinensis de histor. tobie
            <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>c. 40.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e583">Esto pacificus: fuge iurgia vincula <unclear>pac</unclear>
            <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>Celica sunt anime pocula: corpus alunt.
            <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>Plausus alit gentes.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-d1e593">
          <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Rd1e681">Prouerb. vulgar:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34897-Qd1e597">Rason mete pace.
            <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>Chi non se vole enganare tosto sacorda.
            <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>Beato se proua chi in pace se troua.</quote>
        </p>
